scoringPlays.text: Kerryon Johnson 60 Yd Run (Daniel Carlson Kick)
Tomarcio Reese 22 Yd Fumble Return (Tyler Bass Kick)
Jarrett Stidham 14 Yd Run (Daniel Carlson Kick)
Kam Martin 36 Yd Run (Daniel Carlson Kick)
Ryan Davis 19 Yd pass from Jarrett Stidham (Daniel Carlson Kick)
Will Hastings 19 Yd pass from Jarrett Stidham (Daniel Carlson Kick)

videos.headline: Auburn scores on opening drive with a FG

videos.description: Kerryon Johnson takes the hand off and streaks down the sideline for a 60-yard TD in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Johnson's TD run extends Auburn's lead

videos.description: Jay Bowdry makes a nice diving grab to intercept Jarrett Stidham's pass.
videos.headline: Georgia Southern makes leaping interception

videos.description: Chris DeLaRosa sacks Jarrett Stidham and forces the fumble. Tomarcio Reese returns it  22 yards for the TD.
videos.headline: Georgia Southern's sack and fumble recovery results in TD

videos.description: Tomarcio Reese gets injured on 34-yard run, gets up on his own power and limps to sideline.
videos.headline: Kerryon Johnson gets injured on a run, gets up on his own power

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham runs for 14-yards to score Auburn TD.
videos.headline: Auburn QB Jarrett Stidham runs for TD

videos.description: Kam Martin runs for 36 yards for a TD to extend Auburn's lead.
videos.headline: Auburn widens lead with rushing TD

videos.description: Gus Malzahn recounts first half mistakes and what needs to be fixed for Auburn.
videos.headline: Auburn Head Coach Guz Malzahn discusses adjustments for Auburn

videos.description: Davis breaks tackle and dives into end zone to get TD for Auburn.
videos.headline: Auburn Ryan Davis dives into end zone for TD

videos.description: Marlon Davidson tackles Shai Werts for loss of 9  yards making it Auburns 5th sack of the night.
videos.headline: Auburn gets its 5th sack of the night

videos.description: Auburn's Will Hastings jumps and flips during a 15-yard run to avoid tackle.
videos.headline: Hastings with an impressive flip to avoid tackle

videos.description: Kam Martin breaks off an impressive 61-yard run.
videos.headline: Kam Martin makes explosive run for Auburn

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham connects with Will Hastings for deep TD.
videos.headline: Stidham adds to Auburn's lead with deep TD pass

videos.description: Head Coach Guz Malzahn pleased with Auburns home opener and ready for Clemson next week.
videos.headline: Auburn Head Coach Guz Malzahn looking to Clemson face off after tonight's win

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham on  his first start in two years and what needs to improve for upcoming Clemson game.
videos.headline: Auburn QB Jarrett Stidham pleased first start in two years

videos.description: Derrick Brown explains how he prepared for this game and other future games coming this season.
videos.headline: Auburn DL Derrick Brown preparation for the season

videos.description: Jordan Rodgers and Tom Hart discuss the pressure of Auburn starting QB Jarrett Stidham.
videos.headline: Post game coverage of Auburn blowout against Georgia Southern
